            <p><strong>Your Consent:</strong> By using our services, you consent to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. If you do not agree with our policies and practices, please do not use our services.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2><i class="fas fa-database"></i> 2. Information We Collect</h2>
