            <li><strong>Register for an account:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, company name, and other contact information</li>
            <li><strong>Use our services:</strong> Project requirements, preferences, feedback, and communications</li>
            <li><strong>Contact us:</strong> Information provided through contact forms, support requests, or customer service interactions</li>
