            <li><strong>Withdraw Consent:</strong> Withdraw consent where processing is based on consent</li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information provided in the "Contact Us" section below. We will respond to your request within a reasonable timeframe and in accordance with applicable law.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
